---
description: Dependency and package upgrade rules
globs: package.json,pnpm-lock.yaml,_contract/dependency-policy.md,_drift/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Read `_contract/dependency-policy.md` before adding or upgrading packages.

- No random dependencies; no overlapping UI libraries
- No framework major upgrades during feature work
- Fork pins go in `_drift/dependency-exceptions.md`
- After changes: `pnpm foundry:verify` and `pnpm test`

Use `prompts/upgrade-dependencies.md` for maintenance passes.
